{"tid":2488242,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"被指旺角站外叫「死黑警」　退休公僕認罪判囚 40 天 並失去部分或全部退休金","createTime":"2021-04-14T05:59:41.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-14T06:50:35.000Z","uid":22556,"like":11,"dislike":60,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"318a47636a377f378ab080dd90fecc3dc2794099","tid":2488242,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T05:59:41.000Z","msg":"去年 6 月 12 日反修例衝突一周年，旺角一帶有人聚集，其中六旬退休漢被指在旺角站外喧嘩或擾亂秩序。他今（14 日）在西九龍裁判法院承認在公眾地方作出擾攘秩序行為罪，被判囚 40 天。主任裁判官徐綺薇認為，被告帶頭叫口號，屬領導角色，令現場氣氛更見緊張，甚至引發暴力風險，故即使被告事發後寢食難安，更很可能因此失去部分或全部退休金，都決定判處監禁。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/court/%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87%E6%97%BA%E8%A7%92%E7%AB%99%E5%A4%96%E5%8F%AB-%E6%AD%BB%E9%BB%91%E8%AD%A6-%E9%80%80%E4%BC%91%E5%85%AC%E5%83%95%E8%AA%8D%E7%BD%AA%E5%88%A4%E5%9B%9A-40-%E5%A4%A9-%E5%AE%98-%E5%B8%B6%E9%A0%AD%E5%8F%AB%E5%8F%A3%E8%99%9F%E5%BC%95%E6%9A%B4%E5%8A%9B%E9%A2%A8%E9%9A%AA/?fbclid=IwAR1cCLnb76BRLCeXyCEc83Qr6Dwo2nj0ivUCwoDOg40qooraZ7K4rIjA1Xs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258C%2587%25E6%2597%25BA%25E8%25A7%2592%25E7%25AB%2599%25E5%25A4%2596%25E5%258F%25AB-%25E6%25AD%25BB%25E9%25BB%2591%25E8%25AD%25A6-%25E9%2580%2580%25E4%25BC%2591%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%2583%2595%25E8%25AA%258D%25E7%25BD%25AA%25E5%2588%25A4%25E5%259B%259A-40-%25E5%25A4%25A9-%25E5%25AE%2598-%25E5%25B8%25B6%25E9%25A0%25AD%25E5%258F%25AB%25E5%258F%25A3%25E8%2599%259F%25E5%25BC%2595%25E6%259A%25B4%25E5%258A%259B%25E9%25A2%25A8%25E9%259A%25AA%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1cCLnb76BRLCeXyCEc83Qr6Dwo2nj0ivUCwoDOg40qooraZ7K4rIjA1Xs&d=t2%2FAN0mLur8%2Bj%2B1TvbkzvgUT8Qe%2F7ZKEe33%2FbaB1Hos%3D&h=c800d234\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258C%2587%25E6%2597%25BA%25E8%25A7%2592%25E7%25AB%2599%25E5%25A4%2596%25E5%258F%25AB-%25E6%25AD%25BB%25E9%25BB%2591%25E8%25AD%25A6-%25E9%2580%2580%25E4%25BC%2591%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%2583%2595%25E8%25AA%258D%25E7%25BD%25